ive information about the DNS zone.\n\n## Summary\nThe domain is fully hosted on **Cloudflare** infrastructure with email services through **Google Workspace**. The setup is standard and secure with proper SPF configuration for email authentication."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1850,"cache_read_input_tokens":15275,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1850,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":621,"service_tier":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CWs1w6vn7GYbinhLrDjzZ","type":"assistant","uuid":"7ee12f65-b1f0-4a5a-bf5c-c4907929ef3a","timestamp":"2026-01-06T23:47:24.569Z"}
